Sentencas: Electrolyte supported as well as anode supported single-cells based on BaIn0.3Ti0.7O2.85 (BIT) electrolyte were developed.
Titulo: Intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell based on BaIn0.3Ti0.7O2.85 electrolyte

Sentencas: In these cells, Ni-BIT cermet was used as anode and La0.8Sr0.2MnO3 as cathode.
Titulo: Intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell based on BaIn0.3Ti0.7O2.85 electrolyte

Sentencas: Electrolyte supported cells were fabricated by coating slurries of anode and cathode materials on the circular faces of sintered electrolyte discs.
Titulo: Intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell based on BaIn0.3Ti0.7O2.85 electrolyte

Sentencas: The maximum power (P-max) drawn was 15 MW cm(-2) at 30 mA cm(-2).
Titulo: Intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell based on BaIn0.3Ti0.7O2.85 electrolyte

Sentencas: Anode supported cells were fabricated by co-pressing and co-sintering anode and electrolyte powders.
Titulo: Intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell based on BaIn0.3Ti0.7O2.85 electrolyte

Sentencas: The thickness of electrolyte in anode supported cells was reduced to 80 mu m and the area specific resistance decreased considerably.
Titulo: Intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell based on BaIn0.3Ti0.7O2.85 electrolyte

Sentencas: The value of P-max improved to similar to 100 mW cm(-2).
Titulo: Intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell based on BaIn0.3Ti0.7O2.85 electrolyte
